text: I had the pleasure of attending the Huntsville Hospital Foundations Annual Luncheon. It was great to speak with so many community leaders who support our Huntsville Hospital Health Systems, which includes a 15 county region. The foundation supports the hospital system through investments in medical technology and programs that advance and improve the health care provided to our communities. I would like to thank all the healthcare workers, nurses, physicians, etc. for their dedication in providing exceptional care to our region.
